我建议你主 claim 写成三句话：

> **Strong native GUI agents already know where to act, but their knowledge is often trapped in coordinate-generating heads.**
> **We show that this spatial knowledge can be exposed through lightweight coordinate-free adapters.**
> **Moreover, the best spatial signal is layer-dependent, so grounding adapters should learn when and where to read internal representations.**

中文意思是：

> 强 GUI agent 已经有空间知识，但这种知识被坐标输出头“封装”了；我们用轻量 post-training 把它显式读出来，并发现最佳 grounding 信号不是最后层，而是 layer-dependent 的。

这比“我提升了 grounding acc”有意义得多。

