## 8. 损失函数可以围绕“安全执行”重写

不要只写：

$$

\mathcal{L}_{ground}

$$

而是写成：

$$

\mathcal{L}
=
\mathcal{L}_{region}
+
\lambda_v \mathcal{L}_{verify}
+
\lambda_r \mathcal{L}_{reject}
+
\lambda_u \mathcal{L}_{utility}
+
\lambda_c \mathcal{L}_{calib}

$$

### Region posterior

$$

\mathcal{L}_{region}
=
\sum_{l\in\mathcal{L}}
\alpha_l
\mathrm{KL}(y \Vert p^{(l)})

$$

### Verifier

$$

\mathcal{L}_{verify}
=
-\log
\frac{\exp v_{r^+}}
{\sum_{r_i\in\mathcal{R}}\exp v_{r_i}}

$$

### Reject / no-target

$$

\mathcal{L}_{reject}
=
-
y_{\varnothing}\log P_{\varnothing}
-
(1-y_{\varnothing})\log(1-P_{\varnothing})

$$

### Zoom utility

$$

U^\*(a)
=
R_{\text{after}}(a)
-
R_{\text{before}}
-
\beta C(a)
-
\gamma \mathbf{1}[\text{bad zoom}]

$$

$$

\mathcal{L}_{utility}
=
\left(
\hat{U}(a)-U^\*(a)
\right)^2

$$

### Calibration

$$

\mathcal{L}_{calib}
=
\mathrm{BCE}
(
\hat{P}_{correct},
\mathbf{1}[\text{click correct}]
)

$$

最终系统不是只输出一个点，而是输出：

$$

(\text{region}, \text{confidence}, \text{risk}, \text{reject}, \text{zoom decision})

$$

这就很像真实产品要的东西。

