## 11. 我给你的最终推荐架构

最终可以叫：

> **Layer-wise Coordinate-Free Projection Head, LCFP Head**

具体如下：

$$

q^{(l)} = \mathrm{MLP}_q(\mathrm{LN}(h^{(l)}_{\text{GROUND}}))

$$

$$

k^{(l)}_i = \mathrm{MLP}_k(\mathrm{LN}(h^{(l)}_{vis,i}) + \mathrm{LoRA}^{(l)}_v(h^{(l)}_{vis,i}))

$$

$$

z^{(l)}_i =
\frac{q^{(l)\top}k^{(l)}_i}{\sqrt{d'}}
+
b_{\text{2D}}(i)

$$

$$

p^{(l)} = \mathrm{softmax}(z^{(l)})

$$

$$

p_{\text{final}} =
\sum_l
\omega_l p^{(l)}

$$

$$

\omega_l =
\mathrm{softmax}
(
g_\theta(
[
H^{(l)}, m^{(l)}, \mathrm{topk}^{(l)}, \mathrm{JS}^{(l)}, e_l
]
)
)

$$

训练：

$$

\mathcal{L}
=
\mathrm{KL}(y\Vert p_{\text{final}})
+
\lambda
\sum_l
\alpha_l
\mathrm{KL}(y\Vert p^{(l)})

$$

部署：

$$

\hat r =
\mathrm{TopComponent}(p_{\text{final}})

$$

$$

\hat c =
\mathrm{Center}(\hat r)

$$

或者：

$$

\hat c =
\sum_i p_{\text{final},i} c_i

$$

