# 七、最终论文一句话版本

整篇工作现在可以浓缩成：

> **We diagnose the coordinate bottleneck in native GUI agents: their strongest patch-level grounding evidence often appears before the final coordinate-generation layers. Instead of reading raw attention or fine-tuning the full model, we freeze existing coordinate-generating GUI agents and train lightweight layer-wise coordinate-free projection heads. These heads use the pre-coordinate action-prefix hidden state as a query to read spatial evidence from intermediate visual tokens, producing a safer and more accurate grounding interface with minimal post-training.**

中文版本：

> 我们诊断 native GUI agent 中的坐标生成瓶颈：最强的 patch-level grounding 证据常常出现在最终坐标生成层之前。我们不直接读取原始 attention，也不完整微调模型，而是冻结已有坐标生成型 GUI agent，并训练轻量级逐层 coordinate-free projection head。该 head 使用坐标生成前的 action-prefix hidden state 作为 query，从中间层视觉 token 中读出空间证据，从而以极低后训练成本获得更安全、更准确的 grounding interface。

这版现在逻辑更完整了：

$$

\text{coordinate-generating agent}
\rightarrow
\text{pre-coordinate query}
\rightarrow
\text{middle-layer visual hidden states}
\rightarrow
\text{coordinate-free posterior}
\rightarrow
\text{safe grounding retrofit}

$$

它也避免了最危险的设计问题：**错误地把坐标 token 或未监督 attention 当作 grounding query。**